General.Name: Nova Minerals Limited
General.Description: Nova Minerals Limited engages in the exploration of mineral properties in Australia and the United States. The company explores for gold deposits. Its flagship project is the Estelle Gold project that covers an area of 514 square kilometers located in the State of Alaska. The company was formerly known as Quantum Resources Limited and changed its name to Nova Minerals Limited in December 2017. Nova Minerals Limited was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Caulfield, Australia.
